    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/611a22a41144daae0e4048cb0be9d17b.avif?t=1732083604\" width=800 height=302 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个2d卡通风格，以未来太空战争为背景的回合对战游戏，玩家扮演一名太空船舰长，不断完善太空船的建设，并抵御入侵者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/5e236fe2925b6a9fbf01e550f59b0fdf.avif?t=1732083604\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的目标就是保护你的飞船核心不被敌人摧毁，并且摧毁敌人的核心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/d20c4a657ff7d3c8f529b299de3aaa22.poster.avif?t=1732083604\" width=600 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/d20c4a657ff7d3c8f529b299de3aaa22.webm?t=1732083604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/d20c4a657ff7d3c8f529b299de3aaa22.mp4?t=1732083604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/3c63dbae2f2920bfa592735b6b590a7f.avif?t=1732083604\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在商店购买并合成更高级的装备，提升飞船的战斗力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/a634a9cbd4550e1e74fed275297e0f36.poster.avif?t=1732083604\" width=600 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/a634a9cbd4550e1e74fed275297e0f36.webm?t=1732083604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/a634a9cbd4550e1e74fed275297e0f36.mp4?t=1732083604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/86e86b321a99515deaa40d2a05fa84d6.avif?t=1732083604\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择合适的装备，制定策略，放置合适的位置，迎接接下来的战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/500a6ee1b32c3313599423be712f8a5c.poster.avif?t=1732083604\" width=600 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/500a6ee1b32c3313599423be712f8a5c.webm?t=1732083604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/500a6ee1b32c3313599423be712f8a5c.mp4?t=1732083604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/19dabf82d30b182809d585c46f3784af.avif?t=1732083604\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找旗鼓相当的对手与之战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042640/extras/9cb454b589c6c99a7d92098ded1fd2be.poster.avif?t=1732083604\" width=600 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042